sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant A as Agent Runtime
    participant S as kit/skills/*/SKILL.md
    participant M as kit/core-zero/memories/repo
    participant F as artifacts/features/<slug>

    U->>A: Invocation command / request
    A->>S: Read active SKILL.md (workflow, boundaries, stop conditions)
    S-->>A: Skill guidelines and rules
    A->>M: Read MASTER_INDEX.md and load memories (always + by-intent)
    M-->>A: Repo guidelines, constraints, heuristics, specs
    A->>F: Read active feature state (status, spec, plan, tasks, handoff)
    F-->>A: Current phase state and checklist
    A->>A: Execute task steps and run proof/test commands
    A->>F: Write/update feature artifacts (spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md, progress.md)
    opt Post-Ship Sync (on verify Pass)
        A->>M: Sync and update memories (learned-heuristics.md, PKB, core-policies.md)
    end
    A->>F: Update status.md and write handoff.md (on session end)
    A-->>U: Return status, completion checklist, and verification outcomes

    Note over A,F: Guided feature delivery lifecycle:<br/>/starter-init -> /context-session START -> /spec-research -> /spec-requirements -> /spec-plan -> /spec-implement -> /harness-verify -> /context-session END
